l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收平啲咪有需要囉"},{"pid":"81f06a3e0d80ac7e1ce1cffff3a679b2c4cd5623","tid":301504,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要預畢業後人工好低，可能得萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非牟利獸醫服務協會執行主席麥志豪表示，新入行獸醫月薪中位數為3萬元，經3至4年時間累積經驗，月入可達6位數字、即10萬元。<br />\n<br />\nOn9仔鳩吹</blockquote><br />\n之前教資會報告就係講唔批獸醫係因為香港冇咁大需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收平啲咪有需要囉</blockquote><br />\n獸醫冇需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把人當正d貓狗係自己仔女"},{"pid":"206083e5d4bb6a2e9a18f7218d55c3fbfe56a37d","tid":301504,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:36:44.000Z","msg":"有呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d18bbb3c407972a336aae85d7cfc0546209315d","tid":301504,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要預畢業後人工好低，可能得萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非牟利獸醫服務協會執行主席麥志豪表示，新入行獸醫月薪中位數為3萬元，經3至4年時間累積經驗，月入可達6位數字、即10萬元。<br />\n<br />\nOn9仔鳩吹</blockquote><br />\n之前教資會報告就係講唔批獸醫係因為香港冇咁大需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收平啲咪有需要囉</blockquote><br />\n獸醫冇需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把人當正d貓狗係自己仔女</blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n而家越黎越多人養貓狗代替生仔，需求只會越黎越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2a1f2ea0e32a169b672a7e8c44e844b2b811eb","tid":301504,"uid":67447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要預畢業後人工好低，可能得萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非牟利獸醫服務協會執行主席麥志豪表示，新入行獸醫月薪中位數為3萬元，經3至4年時間累積經驗，月入可達6位數字、即10萬元。<br />\n<br />\nOn9仔鳩吹</blockquote><br />\n之前教資會報告就係講唔批獸醫係因為香港冇咁大需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收平啲咪有需要囉</blockquote><br />\n獸醫冇需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把人當正d貓狗係自己仔女</blockquote><br />\n點會冇需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而係太少同太唔可靠<br />\n香港動保條例好落後 獸醫鳩醫死左你隻野 係冇任何法律責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果開左呢科 政府都要更新下d法例先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc24cdcf15b4735c5b4622d57d6a85f29ea3db","tid":301504,"uid":72566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:42:27.000Z","msg":"重點係自資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  讀唔讀得起都成問題 <br />\n讀完獸醫最緊要都係睇你profile <br />\n我見啲鬼佬獸醫好多時都要去啲野生動物保護區呀個啲度做 返到黎先吃香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3bb7d177636204224616ebc48f631a6dd5ce70","tid":301504,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"海外已經有幾十所大學獸醫學生可以係香港註冊，政府同獸醫業界每年都講行內夠人，獸醫比例好高，可以search下新聞<br />\n<br />\n雖然PT,OT個個話爆煲，但冇官方人士會咁講，反而獸醫就會"},{"pid":"7a5b268fbe62b3badb0f81f8fbf83c0de135e737","tid":301504,"uid":93903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"72萬讀6年，屋企有家底先好諗，仲要出黎唔知有冇人請"},{"pid":"9600d54696accad9b1609cd8b6a4326a069c9e80","tid":301504,"uid":93903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"啲報告成日話外國既人手比例點點點<br />\n外國人手比例係點關香港叉事咩<br />\n香港人包埋香港政府永遠都係用最少錢去維持機構營運既 <br />\n學店錢就識收喇 就業話知你"},{"pid":"907e6da4ecbb59ab416b88a1f9a17924984d05db","tid":301504,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>72萬讀6年，屋企有家底先好諗，仲要出黎唔知有冇人請</blockquote><br />\n可以做動物相關醫學研究，仲要係獨市，可能前途好好<br />\n<br />\n如果要執業，就要有心理準備付出同回報不成正比，畢業後人工唔會高<br />\n<br />\n不過好多人都係講熱誠或者本身有家底，應該唔會計較錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb09e906bbae61961deac05fdc1e9b031aec4c49","tid":301504,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:12:31.000Z","msg":"一句講哂<br />\n假設你帶隻寵物要睇獸醫<br />\n澳洲/英帝grad<br />\n台大grad<br />\nShitty grad<br />\n你會揀邊個"},{"pid":"a375ca9e163d2d54e97bdc36098d965992ca5167","tid":301504,"uid":101341,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一句講哂<br />\n假設你帶隻寵物要睇獸醫<br />\n澳洲/英帝grad<br />\n台大grad<br />\nShitty grad<br />\n你會揀邊個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCity 同康奈爾合辦 康奈爾大學獸醫全球排名第一 柒少陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eb9427979ba21245e554fe5a4fcc1654933d29","tid":301504,"uid":77816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"香港冇乜獸醫診所，<br />\n全部都係私人，<br />\n冇得打工，<br />\n讀完仲要預錢開診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d075acadacb05faeb5be6135f7ba2c1e71a7ca20","tid":301504,"uid":101341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港冇乜獸醫診所，<br />\n全部都係私人，<br />\n冇得打工，<br />\n讀完仲要預錢開診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/111450_4eddd37f83ce55dc3ff008188c660336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F111450_4eddd37f83ce55dc3ff008188c660336.jpg&h=2fa9149e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86e04032051bfe640595bd37c938acd0c697f153","tid":301504,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港冇乜獸醫診所，<br />\n全部都係私人，<br />\n冇得打工，<br />\n讀完仲要預錢開診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能呢方面遲下成熟啲<br />\n會多啲寵物醫院"},{"pid":"bdc97ea4ea4528124480bc7ff71bb65781de894c","tid":301504,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港冇乜獸醫診所，<br />\n全部都係私人，<br />\n冇得打工，<br />\n讀完仲要預錢開診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/111450_4eddd37f83ce55dc3ff008188c660336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F111450_4eddd37f83ce55dc3ff008188c660336.jpg&h=2fa9149e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個post都唔知有幾多個位, 仲要成堆外國讀完返黎爭<br />\n<br />\n真係有興趣去讀無問題既, 為賺錢既真係唔值囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}